2773.NL: if A has a husband B, B has a son C, C has a son D, D has a aunt E, and A is female, E is female, then E is the grandson of A.
2773.FOL: husband(A, B) ^ son(B, C) ^ son(C, D) ^ aunt(D, E) ^ female(A) ^ female(E) => grandson(A, E)

2774.NL: if A has a son B, B has a wife C, C has a son D, D has a aunt E, and A is male, E is female, then E is the daughter-in-law of A.
2774.FOL: son(A, B) ^ wife(B, C) ^ son(C, D) ^ aunt(D, E) ^ male(A) ^ female(E) => daughter-in-law(A, E)

2775.NL: if A has a sister B, B has a son C, C has a brother D, D has a grandmother E, and A is female, E is female, then E is the father-in-law of A.
2775.FOL: sister(A, B) ^ son(B, C) ^ brother(C, D) ^ grandmother(D, E) ^ female(A) ^ female(E) => father-in-law(A, E)
